{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892724742,"sessionID":"ses_2848c4100ffe5LtG4M55bByBGV","part":{"id":"prt_d7b7477ad0015sTjl6jct7yWwE","messageID":"msg_d7b7463df001qe8UvVh7m37E9b","sessionID":"ses_2848c4100ffe5LtG4M55bByBGV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n2: \n3: 要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n4: \n5: ## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n6: - **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n7: - **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n8: - **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n9: \n10: ## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n11: - **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n12: - **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n13: - **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n14: \n15: ## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n16: - **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n17: - **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n18: \n19: ## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n20: - **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。\n21: - **TestCase-PD-002**: 错误处理。发送语法错误代码，预期 stderr 包含 `SyntaxError`。\n22: \n23: ## 5. Python SDK 测试\n24: - **TestCase-SDK-001**: 上下文管理器验证。使用 `with CodeInterpreterClient(...) as client:` 确保结束时自动调用 `close()`。\n25: - **TestCase-SDK-002**: 异常映射。服务端返回 500 时，SDK 抛出自定义 `AgentCubeError` 而非原始 HTTP 错误。\n26: \n27: ## 实施要求\n28: - **Go 代码**：必须位于对应的 `*_test.go` 中，可通过 `go test ./...` 运行。\n29: - **Python 代码**：必须位于 `tests/` 目录或 `test_*.py` 文件中，可通过 `pytest` 运行。\n\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n\n要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n\n## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n- **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n\n## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n- **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n- **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n- **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n\n## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n- **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n- **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n\n## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n- **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md","time":{"start":1775892724729,"end":1775892724740}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892724756,"sessionID":"ses_2848c4100ffe5LtG4M55bByBGV","part":{"id":"prt_d7b7472e9001njX7ekqZcPhirF","messageID":"msg_d7b7463df001qe8UvVh7m37E9b","sessionID":"ses_2848c4100ffe5LtG4M55bByBGV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/tests.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/tests.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Test Specification\n2: \n3: ## Unit Tests\n4: \n5: ### Execution Client Tests\n6: - [ ] `test_submit_execution_success` - Verify successful execution submission\n7: - [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_agent` - Handle agent not found error\n8: - [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_input` - Handle invalid input error\n9: - [ ] `test_get_status_pending` - Query pending execution status\n10: - [ ] `test_get_status_running` - Query running execution status\n11: - [ ] `test_get_status_completed` - Query completed execution status\n12: - [ ] `test_get_status_failed` - Query failed execution status\n13: - [ ] `test_get_result_success` - Fetch execution results\n14: - [ ] `test_get_result_not_ready` - Handle result not ready error\n15: - [ ] `test_retry_on_transient_error` - Verify retry logic\n16: \n17: ### Input Parser Tests\n18: - [ ] `test_parse_json_string_input` - Parse JSON string inputs\n19: - [ ] `test_parse_key_value_input` - Parse key=value pairs\n20: - [ ] `test_parse_file_input` - Parse JSON file input\n21: - [ ] `test_parse_merged_inputs` - Merge multiple input sources\n22: - [ ] `test_parse_invalid_json` - Handle invalid JSON\n23: - [ ] `test_parse_file_not_found` - Handle missing file\n24: \n25: ### Formatter Tests\n26: - [ ] `test_format_json_output` - Format response as JSON\n27: - [ ] `test_format_table_output` - Format response as table\n28: - [ ] `test_format_status_colors` - Apply color coding to status\n29: - [ ] `test_format_empty_result` - Handle empty results\n30: \n31: ### Invoke Command Tests\n32: - [ ] `test_invoke_async_success` - Async invoke returns execution ID\n33: - [ ] `test_invoke_sync_success` - Sync invoke waits and returns result\n34: - [ ] `test_invoke_sync_timeout` - Handle sync timeout\n35: - [ ] `test_invoke_with_file_input` - Invoke with file input\n36: - [ ] `test_invoke_with_json_input` - Invoke with JSON input\n37: - [ ] `test_invoke_with_kv_input` - Invoke with key-value input\n38: - [ ] `test_invoke_agent_not_found` - Handle agent not found\n39: - [ ] `test_invoke_invalid_input` - Handle invalid input parameters\n40: \n41: ### Status Command Tests\n42: - [ ] `test_status_query_success` - Query execution status\n43: - [ ] `test_status_not_found` - Handle execution not found\n44: - [ ] `test_status_watch_mode` - Test continuous polling\n45: - [ ] `test_status_completed_exit` - Exit code 0 when completed\n46: - [ ] `test_status_failed_exit` - Exit code 3 when failed\n47: \n48: ## Integration Tests\n49: \n50: ### Workflow Tests\n51: - [ ] `test_invoke_then_status` - Invoke agent and check status\n52: - [ ] `test_invoke_sync_full_workflow` - Complete sync workflow\n53: - [ ] `test_invoke_async_poll_until_complete` - Poll until completion\n54: \n55: ### Error Handling Tests\n56: - [ ] `test_network_error_handling` - Handle network failures\n57: - [ ] `test_auth_error_handling` - Handle authentication failures\n58: - [ ] `test_server_error_handling` - Handle server errors\n59: \n60: ## E2E Tests\n61: \n62: ### Happy Path\n63: - [ ] `test_e2e_invoke_async_agent` - End-to-end async invocation\n64: - [ ] `test_e2e_invoke_sync_agent` - End-to-end sync invocation\n65: - [ ] `test_e2e_status_tracking` - Track execution status\n66: \n67: ### Edge Cases\n68: - [ ] `test_e2e_large_input` - Handle large input payloads\n69: - [ ] `test_e2e_long_running` - Handle long-running executions\n70: - [ ] `test_e2e_concurrent_invocations` - Multiple concurrent invokes\n71: \n72: ## Test Data Requirements\n73: \n74: ### Mock Agent\n75: - Simple echo agent for testing\n76: - Agent with required parameters\n77: - Agent with optional parameters\n78: \n79: ### Mock Responses\n80: - Pending status response\n81: - Running status response\n82: - Completed status with result\n83: - Failed status with error message\n\n(End of file - total 83 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Execution Client Tests\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_success` - Verify successful execution submission\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_agent` - Handle agent not found error\n- [ ] `test_submit_execution_invalid_input` - Handle invalid input error\n- [ ] `test_get_status_pending` - Query pending execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_running` - Query running execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_completed` - Query completed execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_status_failed` - Query failed execution status\n- [ ] `test_get_result_success` - Fetch execution results\n- [ ] `test_get_result_not_ready` - Handle result not ready error\n- [ ] `test_retry_on_transient_error` - Verify retry logic\n\n### Input Parser Tests\n- [ ] `test_parse_json_string_input` - Parse JSON string inputs\n- [ ] `test_parse_key_value_input` - Parse key=value pairs\n- [ ] `test_parse_file_input` - Parse JSON file input","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-023/tests.md","time":{"start":1775892724724,"end":1775892724753}}}}
